Changes:
 user-installed-packages (26.05.3) mx; urgency=medium
 .
   * Fix changelog display crash on newer yad 14.x (write to tempfile, use --filename)
   * Fix icon resolution: use full path when icon file exists
   * Fix xfce4-terminal invocation on Fluxbox (SESSION_MANAGER empty)
   * Add CLI interface: --generate, --install, --cli, --help, --version flags
   * Add bash completion for all CLI options
   * Add gettext/ngettext wrapper for automatic bad-char sanitization
   * Translations refresh
